		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
		font-weight: 400;
		flex: 1;
	}

	.card-tech {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		padding-top: 1.5rem;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
